<h2 id="the-research-workflow">The Research Workflow</h2>

<p>While it‚Äôs less common for us to talk about research processes in the humanities and humanistic social sciences than in many STEM fields, it‚Äôs worth thinking about what your research process looks like and where and how you might benefit from tweaking it or incorporating a digital tool.</p>

