  <p><strong>REFLECT</strong><br />
Think about the recent research projects that you‚Äôve worked on. This could be a seminar paper, part of an article, a paper for a conference, etc. Where were your biggest frustrations? Where were the annoyances or sources of friction that kept you from focusing on the work that you wanted to be doing?</p>
